snippet.textDisplay:
Makes me realize,

.... all we ever did, was chase a mirage, leaving a reality behind. The reality, which had hardships, tears, pain but it also had peace, warmth and belonging. 

We left all that, looking for something, that doesn't exist. And now we are so far from our innocence. All we found was, games, treachery, chase, dissatisfaction, false hopes and more chase.

Gone are the days of open fields and simple lives, welcome 21st century, where your technology, not only dig deep Wells but also dug deeper holes in our hearts, never to be filled with anything anymore.
